  <summary date="2021-05-04T14:16:46Z" status="Introduced in House">Honoring All Veterans Act

This bill adds the following as a mission statement for the Department of Veterans Affairs: "To fulfill President Lincoln's promise to care for those 'who shall have borne the battle' and for their families, caregivers, and survivors."</summary>
